小編之前聽說油價與股價之間有連動關係，油價跌，大盤崩，差點要把油價當作明燈了，但是小編膽小，所以只好先用R來觀察一下情況…

第一步當然要下載資料啦～～股價我們在R裡可以用quantmod這個套件，可是原油價格在quantmod中似乎沒有相對應的工具啊……這時候就可以用Quandl下載原油價格囉！

library(Quandl)
library(quantmod)
oil <- Quandl("DOE/RBRTE", type="xts")
getSymbols("^TWII",from="2001-01-01")
## [1] "TWII"

在這邊DOE/RBRTE是布蘭特原油油價在Quandl的代碼，小編也是找了一陣子才找到這個代碼，為了方便大家Quandl有整理出各種標的的代碼表：

https://www.quandl.com/blog/api-for-commodity-data

而^TWII則是台灣加權指數在Yahoo Finance的代碼。有關股票的代碼，其實只要上英文版的Yahoo Finance都可以打關鍵字找到。

接下來可以先畫圖看看，對照一下是不是油價與股價這麼Match～

oil_compare=function(oil="DOE/RBRTE",stock="^TWII",ylab='Europe
                     Brent Crude Oil Spot FOB',days=NULL){
  oil <- Quandl(oil, type="xts")
  TWII=getSymbols(stock,from="2001-01-01",auto.assign = FALSE)
  oil_date=as.character(index(oil))
  TWII_date=as.character(index(TWII))
  intersect_date=intersect(oil_date,TWII_date)
  if (is.null(days)){
    TWII_cor=TWII[intersect_date]
    oil_cor=oil[intersect_date]
  }else{
    TWII_cor=TWII[tail(intersect_date,days)]
    oil_cor=oil[tail(intersect_date,days)]
  }
  
  # layout(matrix(c(2,1), nrow = 1), widths = c(0.7, 0.3))
  par(mar = c(5, 4, 4, 5) + 0.1)
  plot(1:3, rnorm(3), pch = 1, lty = 1, ylim=c(-2,2), type = "n", axes = FALSE, ann = FALSE)
    legend(0.7,3,col=c("red","black"),lty=1,text.font=2,legend=c("Oil Price",stock),xpd=TRUE,bty='n',lwd=4)
    par(new=TRUE)
    # par(mar=c(5,4,4,5)+.1)
  plot(oil_cor,,main='',ylab=ylab,type = 'n')
  lines(oil_cor,col=2)
  par(new=TRUE)
  plot(Cl(TWII_cor),xaxt="n",yaxt="n",
       main=c('correlation:',as.character(cor(Cl(TWII_cor),oil_cor))))
  axis(4)
  mtext(stock,side=4,line=3)
  
}

oil_compare()

n{r} oil_compare(oil="DOE/RBRTE",stock="2618.TW",days=240) oil_compare(oil="OPEC/ORB",stock="2618.TW")
